<bibRefCitation author="Pleijel, F" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Natural History" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="3543 - 3544" title="Book Review" volume="39" year="2005">Pleijel 2005</bibRefCitation>
). Reported from the Mediterranean, European Atlantic coasts and South Africa, considered questionable in Turkey by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cinar, Melih Ertan" journalOrPublisher="Turkish Journal of Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 31" title="Check-List of Annelida from the Coasts of Turkey" volume="38" year="2014">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Çınar">Cinar</normalizedToken>
et al. (2014)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
